<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 18:18:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>博世首席执行官认为全球汽车市场增长停滞</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bosch-chief-sees-stagnating-growth-car-markets-worldwide-2024-09-17/</link><description>德国汽车供应商博世首席执行官斯特凡·哈同（Stefan Hartung）在接受路透社采访时表示，预计今年和明年全球汽车和商用车市场的增长幅度很小。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 15:21:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bosch-chief-sees-stagnating-growth-car-markets-worldwide-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国保险经纪公司元宝在投资者兴趣复苏之际申请美国首次公开募股</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinese-insurance-broker-yuanbao-files-us-ipo-amid-reviving-investor-appetite-2024-09-17/</link><description>中国保险经纪公司元宝周二在美国申请首次公开募股，这表明投资者对新上市的兴趣全面复苏。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 15:10:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinese-insurance-broker-yuanbao-files-us-ipo-amid-reviving-investor-appetite-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>德拉吉表示，欧盟必须在与中国的清洁技术贸易上找到适当的平衡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/eu-must-find-right-balance-clean-tech-trade-with-china-says-draghi-2024-09-17/</link><description>马里奥·德拉吉周二表示，依靠中国提供绿色产品可能是欧盟实现其气候雄心的最便宜途径，但欧盟需要对中国政府支持的竞争对手做出细致入微的反应，以保留自己的清洁技术工作岗位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 14:28:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/eu-must-find-right-balance-clean-tech-trade-with-china-says-draghi-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>德国哈贝克呼吁政治解决与中国的电动汽车关税争端</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germanys-habeck-calls-political-solution-ev-tariff-dispute-with-china-2024-09-17/</link><description>德国经济部长罗伯特·哈贝克周二在与中国商务部长王文涛会面后呼吁政治解决欧盟与中国之间关于电动汽车关税的争端。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 13:58:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germanys-habeck-calls-political-solution-ev-tariff-dispute-with-china-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国联想将在印度生产人工智能服务器并开设新的以人工智能为中心的实验室</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinas-lenovo-make-ai-servers-india-opens-new-ai-centric-lab-2024-09-17/</link><description>中国电子硬件制造商联想集团周二表示，该公司将开始在印度南部的工厂生产人工智能（AI）服务器，并在班加罗尔科技中心开设一个专注于人工智能服务器的研发实验室。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 12:28:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinas-lenovo-make-ai-servers-india-opens-new-ai-centric-lab-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：新高，美联储与零售健康检查进行轮换</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-09-17/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 10:14:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国称海军飞机过境台湾海峡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-says-navy-aeroplane-transits-taiwan-strait-2024-09-17/</link><description>周二，一架美国海军飞机飞越台湾海峡，美国称这是对自由开放国际空域的承诺，促使中国在其声称拥有的水道上紧急出动战斗机。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 10:09:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-says-navy-aeroplane-transits-taiwan-strait-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国对从中国进口的铀进行调查，以防止规避俄罗斯禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-probes-uranium-jump-china-amid-concerns-over-russian-import-ban-2024-09-17/</link><description>任何规避行为都可能损害美国削减对俄罗斯资金的努力。这也损害了美国建立自己的铀供应链的尝试。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 10:09:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-probes-uranium-jump-china-amid-concerns-over-russian-import-ban-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫表示俄罗斯需要扩大军队以应对西翼日益增长的威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-says-russian-army-expansion-needed-address-growing-threats-western-flank-2024-09-17/</link><description>克里姆林宫周二表示，俄罗斯总统普京需要下令将俄罗斯军队转变为世界第二大军队，以应对俄罗斯西部边境日益增长的威胁和东部的不稳定局势。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 09:49:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-says-russian-army-expansion-needed-address-growing-threats-western-flank-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国告知意大利：欧盟电动汽车调查影响投资者信心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-tells-italy-eu-electric-vehicle-probe-affecting-investor-confidence-2024-09-17/</link><description>中国商务部部长王文涛周一表示，欧盟对中国电动汽车的调查严重影响了中国汽车企业在意大利投资的信心，而区域投票即将进行。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 09:19:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-tells-italy-eu-electric-vehicle-probe-affecting-investor-confidence-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>美银调查显示，降息热潮提振了 9 月份投资者情绪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/rate-cut-fever-boosts-investor-sentiment-september-bofa-survey-shows-2024-09-17/</link><description>美国银行周二公布的基金经理调查显示，由于对美联储软着陆和降息的乐观情绪，9月份全球投资者情绪自6月份以来首次出现改善。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 07:11:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/rate-cut-fever-boosts-investor-sentiment-september-bofa-survey-shows-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>联合国气象机构称，尽管火山喷发，臭氧层仍在恢复中</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/ozone-layer-road-recovery-despite-volcano-eruption-un-weather-body-says-2024-09-17/</link><description>2022年初汤加附近的火山喷发导致去年南极洲上空的臭氧短暂加速消耗，但总体损失有限。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 05:04:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/ozone-layer-road-recovery-despite-volcano-eruption-un-weather-body-says-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国对抗中国的反舰武器战略：充足、机动、致命</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-strategy-anti-ship-weapons-counter-china-plentiful-mobile-deadly-2024-09-17/</link><description>俄罗斯入侵乌克兰将美国推向了这一战略。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 05:04:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-strategy-anti-ship-weapons-counter-china-plentiful-mobile-deadly-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>据英国《金融时报》报道，美国和日本即将达成协议，限制对中国的芯片技术出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-japan-near-deal-curb-chip-technology-exports-china-ft-reports-2024-09-17/</link><description>英国《金融时报》周二援引知情人士的话报道称，尽管东京对北京威胁要报复日本公司发出了警告，但美国和日本即将达成协议，限制对中国芯片行业的技术出口。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 04:22:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-japan-near-deal-curb-chip-technology-exports-china-ft-reports-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>研究显示央行数字货币势头不断增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/central-bank-digital-currency-momentum-growing-study-shows-2024-09-17/</link><description>目前，占全球经济总量 98% 的 134 个国家正在探索本国货币的数字版本，其中近一半国家处于高级阶段，中国、巴哈马和尼日利亚等先驱国家的使用量开始有所增加。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 04:03:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/central-bank-digital-currency-momentum-growing-study-shows-2024-09-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>